snippet.title: Resurgence Returns on New Map Ashika Island | Call of Duty: Warzone 2.0
snippet.description:
Master the way of the warrior #ResurgenceReturns 🌊

Drop into battle on the new Call of Duty #Warzone2 small map Ashika Island launching on February 15 with Season 02. Learn more in the #CODBlog ➡️ https://bit.ly/Ashika-Island
